{"data":[{"date":"08:06 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Monaco 19h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-psg-vs-monaco-19h00-ngay-48-sieu-cup-phap-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG vs Monaco l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Monaco 19h00 ng\u00e0y 48 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Monaco 19h00 ng\u00e0y 48 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/psg-monaco2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Monaco</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>PSG vs Monaco: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>PSG h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu 4 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Thomas Meunier, Kylian Mbappe, Presnel Kimpembe v\u00e0 Alphonse Areola (v\u1eabn ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 sau World Cup 2018). Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Edinson Cavani th\u00ec d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Thomas Tuchel v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Monaco l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i PSG, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Gianluigi Buffon ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn. \u1ede l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean (trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7, Lassana Diarra c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng. Julian Draxler v\u00e0 Angel di Maria c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Monaco t\u1ed1i nay, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1edbi 3-4-3 c\u1ee7a Thomas Tuchel s\u1ebd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh ra sao \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0, Tuchel li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i cho PSG nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u1edbi trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i 3 trung v\u1ec7.\u00a0 3-4-3 hay 3-5-2 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Song, \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap t\u1ed1i nay, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea1m g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u01b0ng \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c: k\u00e9o Layvin Kurzawa l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. V\u1ed1n th\u00edch d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u01b0u th\u1ebf khi ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Monaco. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u may r\u1ee7i. B\u1edfi h\u1ecd t\u1eebng thua 3/4 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y khi ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua Monaco \u1edf 7 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 68% s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ph\u00e1p. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n PSG c\u0169ng th\u1eafng 5/7 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Monaco \u0111\u00e3 tan hoang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi m\u1ea5t 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Fabinho, Thomas Lemar v\u00e0 Joao Moutinho. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 Danijel Subasic v\u1eabn \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 sau World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Falcao kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e2n binh Aleksandr Golovin c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Monaco \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u PSG t\u1ed1i nay v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm c\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7: \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ecdn h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 v\u00e0 thua 2, h\u00f2a 1 \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem ra, PSG c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u Si\u00eau C\u00fap nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, v\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nTheo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG th\u1eafng 5, thua 15 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Monaco th\u1eafng 9, thua 11 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. <br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n trung l\u1eadp, PSG th\u1eafng 2, thua 3 \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Monaco thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMonaco l\u00e9p v\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSG<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1995, Monaco m\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1997 v\u00e0 2000, ngang b\u1eb1ng 3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nantes (1999, 2001), Bordeaux (2008, 2009) v\u00e0 Marseille (2010, 2011). Tuy nhi\u00ean, so v\u1edbi PSG hay Lyon, th\u00ec Monaco c\u00f2n k\u00e9m xa khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Monaco t\u1ed1i nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi: gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ph\u00e1p, v\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG theo \u0111u\u1ed5i 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi<br>\r\nTrong khi ch\u1edd Dortmund g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00e1n Julian Weigl, PSG \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch theo \u0111u\u1ed5i hai m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danilo Pereira (Porto, 26 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Pedrinho (Corinthians, 20 tu\u1ed5i). \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, G\u0110TT Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u00edch Pedrinho v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Corinthians mu\u1ed1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1edbi ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb, PSG v\u1eabn n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o ch\u1ed7 tr\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Thiago Motta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \u201cMonaco lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng th\u00ec h\u1ecd v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch khoan th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jardim\u201d. <br>\r\nHLV Leonardo Jardim (Monaco): \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng PSG. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Monaco s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t may, PSG \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\u201d. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1edbi rung cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n9/10 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, 9/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 6/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Monaco c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 71-90. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trung l\u1eadp c\u1ee7a PSG c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5054","checkdouble":"193686"},{"date":"07:24 04/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 04/08: Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU \u0111\u00f3n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0408-chot-thoi-diem-mu-don-bom-tan-cuoi-cung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 04/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU \u0111\u00f3n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0408 Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU \u0111\u00f3n Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0408 Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU \u0111\u00f3n Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u00f3n Mina v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Gundogan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Song Man xanh \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 fan c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00f4n th\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Pep ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Sarri v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho HLV Chelsea nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ruben Loftus-Cheek s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, hi\u1ec7n HLV Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Crystal Palace b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" title=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/gui-loi-de-nghi-sieu-khung-chelsea-van-bi-tu-choi-vu-zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Hodgson tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Wilfried Zaha kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Roy Hodgson kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng BL\u0110 Crystal Palace s\u1ebd ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eefa ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wilfried Zaha tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Joe Hart?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joe Hart t\u1edbi Burnley l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb Real v\u00e0 M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Morata quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1c ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata \u1edf Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i, thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 29 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span><br>\r\nBarca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o, Pochettino n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mauricio Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Spurs v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5053","checkdouble":"193682"},{"date":"07:57 04/08","title":"Real \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay kh\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/real-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-co-mua-them-tien-dao-hay-khong.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n cho Borja Mayoral.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-quyet-dinh-khong-mua-them-tien-dao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u00f2n Benzema g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca \u1edf La Liga khi\u1ebfn K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra cu\u1ed9c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 CR7, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi kho\u1ea3ng 50 b\u00e0n/m\u00f9a, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng Real bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/them-mot-tien-dao-khung-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid-180-191967.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG</span>, Harry Kane v\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi Real v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema ghi ban vao luoi M.U\" title=\"Benzema ghi ban vao luoi M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Benzema-ghi-ban-vao-luoi-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Benzema\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Cavani, Harry Kane v\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o Karim Benzema, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Borja Mayoral, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Benzema chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Borja Mayoral ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u00d4ng Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5052","checkdouble":"193677"},{"date":"07:05 04/08","title":"Morata quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1c ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/morata-quyet-dinh-soc-ngay-truoc-them-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata \u1edf Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i, thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 29 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017, Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata \u1edf Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata \u1edf Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/So-ao-cua-Alvaro-Morata-o-Chelsea-thay-doi-tu-mua-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu H\u00e8 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/alvaro-morata-van-de-lon-nhat-cua-chelsea-o-mua-giai-toi-172-193634.html\" target=\"_blank\">Morata c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</span>, anh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alvaro Morata \u1edf Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i, thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 29 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 Morata \u0111eo \u1edf Real n\u0103m 2010.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Morata gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch t\u1ea1i sao thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o t\u1eeb 9 l\u00ean 29 l\u00e0 v\u00ec gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Morata v\u00e0 v\u1ee3, Alice Campello chia s\u1ebb tin vui hai c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata o ben ba me con. Anh: NS.\" title=\"Morata \u1edf b\u00ean ba m\u1eb9 con. \u1ea2nh: NS.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tien-dao-morata-don-cap-song-sinh-dau-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o v\u00ec c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc hai thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n ra \u0111\u1eddi. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00f3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i song sinh Alessandro v\u00e0 Leonardo. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4n vinh v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u00eam s\u1ed1 2 v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 mua \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5051","checkdouble":"193676"},{"date":"08:12 04/08","title":"Man City ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/man-city-chi-mua-them-cau-thu-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man xanh ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua\u00a0 Riyad Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester </span>v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man xanh t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pep v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Man-City-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City nh\u1eafm Isco \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City quan t\u00e2m Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi HLV Sarri \u1edf Stamford Bridge thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho bu\u1ed9c Man City ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c, hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Toni Kroos, Isco hay Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real, Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pep n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man xanh ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chi-80-trieu-euro,-Man-City-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Man City mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung nghi\u00eam tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edfi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1eafp kh\u1edfi tranh. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5050","checkdouble":"193678"},{"date":"08:25 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, Darmian ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho c\u1ef1u sao Torino b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Darmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef Darmian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Dalot n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Darmian\" title=\"Matteo Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-307-lo-dien-ben-do-bat-ngo-cua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Matteo Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Darmian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, song th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, ph\u00eda Inter Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Inter Milan th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chuy\u1ec3n sang h\u1ecfi mua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Darmian quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia gi\u1eefa Inter v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5049","checkdouble":"193679"},{"date":"08:11 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Napoli 00h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-napoli-00h00-ngay-58-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool vs Napoli l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Napoli 00h00 ng\u00e0y 58 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Napoli 00h00 ng\u00e0y 58 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Nhan-dinh-Liverpool-vs-Napoli-00h00-ngay-58-Giao-huu-CLB-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Liverpool vs Napoli: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nNgay sau khi thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Klopp - Dortmund v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-3, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Manchester. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a The Kop tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli c\u1ee7a HLV Carlo Ancelotti x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed ti\u1ebfp theo cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, Liverpool lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu hay c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Juventus, Milan, Inter v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool. \u1ede Europa League 2010/11, Napoli c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m/2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Liverpool, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ancelotti, Napoli \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 11 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia (Gozzano, Carpi v\u00e0 Chievo). HLV Ancelotti s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y Napoli d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi, sau 3 n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Simone Verdi, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Napoli t\u1ecf ra \u0111u\u1ed1i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Liverpool v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u. Dries Mertens ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB sau World Cup; c\u00f2n Lorenzo Insigne nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ancelotti c\u1ea5t \u0111i, gi\u1eef g\u00ecn cho ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c Serie A. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y, Napoli c\u00e0ng y\u1ebfm th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Liverpool l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p s\u1ee9c kh\u00e1ng c\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Napoli nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Roma 5-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n The Kop hay d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Italia c\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Napoli c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thua h\u1eb3n Liverpool (c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u CLB Anh kh\u00e1c) v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng duy tr\u00ec nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Ancelotti. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Liverpool: V\u1eafng Oxlade-Chamberlain (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng), Lovren, Henderson, Alexander-Arnold (ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8). <br>\r\n- Napoli: V\u1eafng Meret, Ghoulam, Zielinski, Younes (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng), Mertens (ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8).<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Liverpool th\u1eafng 4, thua 3/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Napoli th\u1eafng 5, thua 9/14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\n3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0 7/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. \u0110\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f9ng ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u01a1n m\u01b0a g\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5048","checkdouble":"193687"},{"date":"20:24 03/08","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Palestine 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c</div>\r\n<h3>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine: 2-1</h3>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Anh \u0110\u1ee9c (45+1), C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (52')<br>\r\nU23 Palestine: Dabbagh (29')\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 29, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 v\u1edbi pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u1ec3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha xoay tr\u1edf trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. 1-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 38 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Ket-qua-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-19h30-ngay-hom-nay-38-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u00edt ph\u00fat, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf trung l\u1ed9, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tung c\u00fa s\u00fat r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi U23 Palestine.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u1ed1n c\u00f3, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. N\u01a1i khung g\u1ed7, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi U23 Palestine, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u00ec l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong vs U23 Palestine\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng vs U23 Palestine\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/congphuong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean hay nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5047","checkdouble":"193660"},{"date":"21:44 03/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong 60 ph\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 33 tu\u1ed5i Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7. Anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Palestine.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, anh l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 ch\u1ea1m g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Palestine.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung, tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Nhung-diem-nhan-tran-dau-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-2-1-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u00ean tay (v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n), C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng. Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng, tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, minh ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng pha ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng, \u0111i b\u00f3ng, b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1eabn r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, m\u00e0u m\u00e8, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n Quang H\u1ea3i, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng n\u00e0o s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng vs U23 Palestine\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/congphuong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y n\u1ed7i lo n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha bay nh\u1ea3y trong khung g\u1ed7, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. V\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u1edf 2 bi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dabbagh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ede pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng. Ph\u00eda trong, c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao, c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd nh\u1eb9 g\u00e1nh \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Ket-qua-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-19h30-ngay-hom-nay-38-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t trong b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nV\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm \u1edf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. R\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Mr. Park \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng &ndash; Anh \u0110\u1ee9c h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi c\u1ea3 2 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn do l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 so s\u00e1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n &ndash; m\u1ed9t H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng (sau V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c) tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 Palestine\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine 2-1<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-325-193664.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/video-tong-hop-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-325-193664.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine (Gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n, c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5046","checkdouble":"193665"},{"date":"23:06 03/08","title":"Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y Park s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 30, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cS\u1edf d\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi e ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch do th\u00e1m. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u1eed 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn quay video. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng lo ng\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Mr. Park c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay: \u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi. \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a C\u0110V. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi V-League \u0111ang b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n\u201d \u2013 HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, khi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 0-0. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Oman v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ket-qua-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-tran-dau-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018-168-193660.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5045","checkdouble":"193667"},{"date":"23:54 03/08","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2><br>\r\nC\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB HAGL, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea1t bi\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/congphuong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh. Khi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi V\u0103n To\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c lao th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u00e1 trung phong. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao trong c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. C\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eafng thua, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, hay xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5044","checkdouble":"193668"},{"date":"00:08 04/08","title":"Vi\u1ec7t Nam ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2015/10/22/hlv-hai-lo-toi-tu-tin-co-the-lam-tot-gdkt-o-doi-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 2-1. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 7 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, v\u00ec v\u1eady chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n, phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0i pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u00fang t\u00fang. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u00d4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palestine\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1eebng ch\u00ea l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a HLV Miura c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/3/28/hlv-hai-lo-lai-khuyen-dt-viet-nam-da-bong-dai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00d4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palestine</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i hay d\u00f9 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t. Pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ebf.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u1ed5 sung cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u00f2n pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tinh t\u1ebf. V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, c\u00f2n V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1eaft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch, r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5043","checkdouble":"193669"},{"date":"20:13 03/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/8: Barca quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-38-barca-quyet-no-bom-tan-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/8.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nBarca quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Pogba<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Hi\u1ec7n nay Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1eadu World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/8 Barca quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 38 Barca quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-38-Barca-quyet-no-bom-tan-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/8: Barca quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Man City tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao tr\u1ebb<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean 112 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Sau khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Jesus c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Courtois<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Hi\u1ec7n nay, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft sao kh\u1ee7ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Bayern Munich, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Arturo Vidal &ndash; m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Paulinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/8\" title=\"tien ve Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/Barca-nham-Arturo-Vidal-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/8: Vidal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Bayern<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi H\u00f9m x\u00e1m, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Anthony Martial v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Robert Lewandowski &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda Bayern c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t k\u1ebft ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Martial h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5042","checkdouble":"193662"}]}